# Intuit Design System - LineHeight Token Library

## Primitive LineHeight Tokens (DO NOT USE DIRECTLY IN PLUGINS)

- `--line-height-120`: 1.2
- `--line-height-130`: 1.3
- `--line-height-140`: 1.4
- `--line-height-150`: 1.5

## Semantic LineHeight Tokens (USE THESE IN PLUGINS)

### Height
- `--line-height-body`: --line-height-150 /* For body text styles (paragraph text) to ensure appropriate line-heights for wrapping text */
- `--line-height-component`: --line-height-130 /* For component text styles to ensure appropriate line-heights for wrapping text */
- `--line-height-display`: --line-height-130 /* For display text styles to ensure appropriate line-heights for wrapping text */
- `--line-height-heading`: --line-height-130 /* For heading text styles to ensure appropriate line-heights for wrapping text */
- `--line-height-mega`: --line-height-120 /* For mega text styles to ensure appropriate line-heights for wrapping text */
